# 9. Most Important Merge Function Logic

### Two Pointer Technique

```text
Left Array  = [1,4,8]

Right Array = [2,3,9]

Compare

1 vs 2 → take 1

4 vs 2 → take 2

4 vs 3 → take 3

4 vs 9 → take 4

8 vs 9 → take 8

Take remaining 9
```

Result

```text
