# 17. Common Mistakes

## Mistake 1

Wrong midpoint

Wrong:

```java
int mid = (low + high) / 2;
```

Better:

```java
int mid = low + (high - low) / 2;
```

---

## Mistake 2

Forgetting Remaining Elements

Wrong:

```java
while(left <= mid && right <= high)
```

Need:

```java
while(left <= mid)

while(right <= high)
```

---

## Mistake 3

Wrong Copy Back

Correct:

```java
arr[i] = temp.get(i - low);
```

